com.ethercis.servicemanager.service

Class ServiceConfigSaxFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ethercis.servicemanager.common.SaxHandlerBase
      • com.ethercis.servicemanager.service.ServiceConfigSaxFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler, org.xml.sax.ext.LexicalHandler

    public class ServiceConfigSaxFactory
extends SaxHandlerBase
    This class parses an xml string to generate a ServiceConfig object. 

      <action do='LOAD'
             onStartupRunlevel='3'
             sequence='5'
             onFail='RESOURCE_CONFIGURATION_PLUGINFAILED'/>
